Trailer For Project Hail Mary in 4K ULTRA HD Quality

Project Hail Mary Plot : Astronaut Ryland Grace wakes up on a space station with no recollection of who he is or what his mission is. As his memory slowly returns, he soon learns that he was sent to the Tau Ceti solar system to reverse the impact of a space event that has already hurled Earth into the early stages of an ice age. As details of the mission unravel, he must call on his scientific training and sheer ingenuity, but he may not have to do it alone.

Cast :
- Ryan Gosling as Dr. Ryland Grace, a sole survivor astronaut who is on a mission to save humanity
- Sandra Hüller as Eva Stratt, Ryland's superior and the head of the Hail Mary project
- Milana Vayntrub as Olesya Ilyukhina, one of the selected astronauts for the crew of the Hail Mary
Lionel Boyce
- Ken Leung as Yáo Li-Jie, another one of the selected astronauts for the crew of the Hail Mary
- Liz Kingsman as Shapiro
- Orion Lee as Xi
- James Ortiz as Rocky, an alien Ry
